<!DOCTYPE html>
%html
  %head
    %meta{charset: "UTF-8"}
    %meta{name: "viewport", content: "width=device-width"}
    %title Bookstore
    %link{href: "https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,400,600", rel: "stylesheet"}
    %link{href: "../css/style.css", rel: "stylesheet"}
  %body
    %header.navbar.navbar-default
      .container
        .navbar-header
          %button.navbar-toggle.pull-left.ml-15{type: "button", 'data-toggle': "collapse", 'data-target': "#navbar"}
            %span.sr-only
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
            %span.icon-bar
          %a.navbar-brand Bookstore
          %a.shop-link.pull-right.visible-xs{href: "#"}
            %span.shop-icon
              %span.shop-quantity 3
        %a.shop-link.pull-right.hidden-xs{href: "#"}
          %span.shop-icon
            %span.shop-quantity 3
        #navbar.navbar-collapse.collapse.pl-30{'aria-expanded': "false"}
          .visible-xs
            %button.close{type: "button", 'aria-label': "Close"}
              %span{'aria-hidden': "true"} &times;
            %ul.nav.navbar-nav
              %li
                %a{href: "#"} Home
              %li
                %a{type: "button", 'data-toggle': "collapse", href: "#menu", 'aria-expanded': "false", 'aria-controls': "menu"} Shop
                %ul#menu.collapse.list-unstyled.pl-30.mb-10{'aria-expanded': "false"}
                  %li
                    %a.collapse-link{href: "#"} Mobile development
                  %li
                    %a.collapse-link{href: "#"} Photo
                  %li
                    %a.collapse-link{href: "#"} Web design
              %li
                %a{href: "#"} My account
          .hidden-xs
            %ul.nav.navbar-nav
              %li
                %a{href: "#"} Home
              %li.dropdown
                %a.dropdown-toggle{href: "#", 'data-toggle': "dropdown", role: "button", 'aria-haspopup': "true", 'aria-expanded': "false"} Shop
                %ul.dropdown-menu
                  %li
                    %a{href: "#"} Mobile development
                  %li
                    %a{href: "#"} Photo
                  %li
                    %a{href: "#"} Web design
                  %li.divider{role: "separator"}
                  %li
                    %a{href: "#"} Log out
              %li
                %a{href: "#"} My account
    %main.container
      %a.general-back-link{href: "#"}
        %i.fa.fa-long-arrow-left.mr-15
        Back to results
      .row
        .col-sm-6
          .product-gallery
            .mb-20
              %img.img-responsive{src: "https://www.bramstein.com/static/smashing-book-5-photo-stack.9d5d114e3e.jpg"}
            .images.clearfix
              %a.img-link{href: "#"}
                %img.width-full{src: "https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg"}
              %a.img-link{href: "#"}
                %img.width-full{src: "https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg"}
              %a.img-link{href: "#"}
                %img.width-full{src: "https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg"}
        .col-sm-6
          %h1.mt-res-0 Real-Life Responsive Web Design
          %p.in-grey-600.small Vitaly Friedman, Daniel Mall,Vitaly Friedman
          .row
            .col-xs-12.col-md-4
              %p.h1.in-gold-500.mt-10 â‚¬32.90
            .col-xs-5.col-md-3
              .input-group.general-position
                %a.input-link{href: "#"}
                  %i.fa.fa-minus.line-height-40
                %input.form-control.quantity-input{type: "text"}
                %a.input-link{href: "#"}
                  %i.fa.fa-plus.line-height-40
            .col-xs-7.col-md-5
              %button.btn.btn-default.pull-right.general-position Add to Cart
          .card
            .clearfix
              %p.general-item-info.pull-right Hardcove, glossy paper
              %p.break-word Materials
            %p.in-grey-600.small.line-height-2
              Smashing Book 5: Real-Life Responsive Web Design is our brand new, upcoming book with smart front-end techniques and design patterns derived from real-life responsive projects. With 13 chapters on responsive workflow, SVG, Flexbox, Web fonts, responsive images, responsive email, content strategy, debugging ...
          .card
            %p Description
            %p.in-grey-600.small.line-height-2
              Smashing Book 5: Real-Life Responsive Web Design is our brand new, upcoming book with smart front-end techniques and design patterns derived from real-life responsive projects. With 13 chapters on responsive workflow, SVG, Flexbox, Web fonts, responsive images, responsive email, content strategy, debugging ...
              %a.in-gold-500.ml-10{href: "#"} Read More
          .card
            .clearfix
              %p.general-item-info.pull-right 2016
              %p.break-word Year of publication
          .card
            .clearfix
              %p.general-item-info.pull-right H:6.4\" x W: 0.9\" x D: 5.0
              %p.break-word Dimensions
          .card
            .clearfix
              %p.general-item-info.pull-right Hardcove, glossy paper
              %p.break-word Materials
      .mb-80
        %h3.in-gold-500.mb-25 Reviews (3)
        %ul.media-list
          %li.media.card
            .media-left
              %a{href: "#"}
                %img.img-circle.logo-size.media-object{src: "https://www.smashingmagazine.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/smashing-book-5-2-large.jpg"}
            .media-body
              %div
                %p.general-message-date.hidden-xs 11/11/16
                %h4.media-heading.max-240.general-message-name
                  %span.general-message-verified Verified Reviewer
                  Rita J. Lewis
              .mb-15
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
              %p Thank you BookStore, I was very pleased to receive my order for the Moleskine diary so soon after placing the order.
          %li.media.card
            .media-left
              %a{href: "#"}
                %span.img-circle.logo-size.logo-empty.media-object M
            .media-body
              %div
                %p.general-message-date.hidden-xs 11/11/16
                %h4.media-heading.max-240.general-message-name
                  %span.general-message-verified Verified Reviewer
                  Rita J. Lewis
              .mb-15
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star
                %i.fa.fa-star.rate-star.rate-empty
              %p Thank you BookStore, I was very pleased to receive my order for the Moleskine diary so soon after placing the order.
